title: Once Upon a Time in China 3 (1992)

sources.title: Once Upon a Time in China 3 (1992)
sources.description:
The Dowager Empress has just decided that the city's best martial arts schools will compete in a grand competition called the Lion Tournament.

Original title: Once Upon a Time in China III
Alternative title: Wong Fei-hung III: Si wong jaang ba (黃飛鴻之三獅王爭霸)

Director: Tsui Hark
Writers: Tsui Hark, Cheung Tan

Main cast:
Jet Li – Wong Fei-hung
Rosamund Kwan – Aunt Yee (Thirteenth Aunt)
Max Mok – Leung Foon
Xiong Xin-Xin (Hung Yan-yan) – Clubfoot
Liu Xun – Viceroy
Yuen Cheung-Yan – Chiu Tin-bak
John Wakefield – Russian Ambassador
Lau Shun – Gov’t Official

Genres: Action, Adventure, History
Release date: 1992 (Hong Kong release: November 19, 1992)
Filming location: Beijing, China (incl. Forbidden City and surrounding areas); Hong Kong
